content.value:
Uber driver: “How long was your flight?”

Me: “2.5 hours”

Driver: “Only 2.5 hours? You look very tired”

Me: “Yep, life beats ya down, man.”

Also, can we stop we stop telling women they look tired? Maybe I don’t feel like a full face of makeup all the time.
